  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for dnsmasq",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for dnsmasq fixes the following issues:\n\nSecurity issues:\n\n- CVE-2023-49441: integer overflow via forward_query (bsc#1226091).\n- CVE-2026-2291: VU#471747: dnsmasq can be abused to record false cached data enabling DoS or attacker redirect\n  (bsc#1258251).\n\nNon security issue:\n\n- Reintroduce nogroup (bsc#1235517).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
